    dc:description "FIGURES 26–28. Scanning electron micrographs of Dorcopsistrongylus supriyatnai n.sp. 26. Cephalic end, apical view. 27. Setate cephalic papillae. 28. Deirid with seta, lateral view. Scale bar: 26, 10 µm; 27, 28, 2 µm" ;
