<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590252>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–25. Dorcopsistrongylus supriyatnai n. sp. 16. Anterior end, ventral view. 17. Buccal capsule, lateral view. 18. Spicule, proximal end, ventral view. 19. Spicule, distal end, lateral view. 20. Genital cone, dorsal view. 21. Gubernaculum, ventral view. 22. Copulatory bursa, dorsal view. 23. Ovejector. 24. Posterior end, lateral view. 25. Egg. Scale bar: 16, 24, 100 µm; 17, 18, 19, 20, 21, 22, 23, 25 µm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2590252/files/figure.png" ;
